import { DataGrid, GridColDef, GridValueGetterParams } from '@mui/x-data-grid'; import '../CSS/keywordCheckTable.css'; export default function KeywordCheckTable(){ const columns: GridColDef[] = [ { field: 'date', headerName: '신청일', width: 80,headerClassName: 'custom-header' }, { field: 'adgoods', headerName: '광고상품', width: 140 }, { field: 'jobfilter', headerName: '작업구분', width: 120 }, { field: 'jobName', headerName: '작업명', width: 100 }, { field: 'jobcondition', headerName: '작업상태', width: 130 }, { field: 'startjob', headerName: '수행시작', width: 130 }, { field: 'endjob', headerName: '수행종료', width: 130 }, { field: 'downloadfile', headerName: '등록파일', width: 130 }, { field: 'downresult', headerName: '결과', width: 130 }, { field: 'downcancel', headerName: '대기취소', width: 130 }, { field: 'requestperson', headerName: '요청자', width: 130 }, ] const rows = [ {id:1, date: '2023-05-17 15:10:50', adgoods: '다음_프리미엄링크', jobfilter:'등록 & 수정', jobName: 'AK몰_다음_등록_PC_230517'}, ]; return(
Dessert (100g serving) Calories Fat (g) Carbs (g) Protein (g) {rows.map((row) => ( {row.name} {row.calories} {row.fat} {row.carbs} {row.protein} ))}
); }
